<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .5in; border: none;"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">若服务器重启，开机后会自行运行程序。</span></p>

<h1 style="border: none;"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">硬件问题</span></h1>
<h2 style="margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span lang="ZH-CN">●<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">狂扫3个相机在系统中显示2个，排查方法</span></strong></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span lang="ZH-CN">○<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">查看电源指示灯，确定摄像头是否正常。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span lang="ZH-CN">○<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">若摄像头工作正常，检查网线是否有网络。</span></p>
<h2 style="margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span lang="ZH-CN">●<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">交叉带阻环不下件，排查方法</span></strong></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span lang="ZH-CN">○<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">检查多少格口红灯亮，若红灯过多，集包人员来不及下货。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span lang="ZH-CN">○<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">异常格口是否解锁，异常快递下不去占用小车。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span lang="ZH-CN">○<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">留盘检测光电是否正常，正常情况一边黄色，绿色，另一边绿色，货物经过时，黄灯熄灭，若两侧均为绿色灯，光电没有配置好。</span></p>
<h2 style="margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span lang="ZH-CN">●<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">若所有设备无法分拣</span></strong><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">。</span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in; text-indent: -.25in; border: none;"><span lang="ZH-CN">○<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">检车服务器和网络情况。</span></p>
<h2 style="margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span lang="ZH-CN">●<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">若部分设备无法分拣</span></strong><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">。</span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span lang="ZH-CN">○<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">与服务器无关，可能原因硬件故障，需要联系供应商电气工程师。</span></p>
<h2 style="margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span lang="ZH-CN">●<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">皮带卡电问题</span></strong></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span lang="ZH-CN">○<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">联系机修。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="border: none;"><span lang="ZH-CN">&nbsp;</span></p>
